content: Just got back from a conference where I presented on AI & ethical trading. Xander's module got some buzz, and I'm buzzing with new ideas for it. Emily's been cooking up a storm, so we're now integrating Xander's AI to suggest vegan recipes with an ethical twist.

Had an awesome time with Emily at our tech pop-up. Xander's AI was key for managing inventory, cutting waste by a solid 30%. Next up, we're getting Xander to help with ethical sourcing for our next gig. Gotta make sure our suppliers are on point!

Xander's now dropping vegan recipes based on ethical sourcing. Emily and I are setting up workshops where you can chat with Xander about AI and sustainability. Oh, and I finally fixed the market prediction model's overfitting problem.

Just tested Xander’s new ethical trading module & it's a game changer! Balancing profit with planet care. Emily and I are hyped for our next pop-up where Xander's AI will make things even cooler with real-time feedback and green tips.
